sections.heading: trauma medical director, defined
sections.text: State trauma medical director means a physician licensed under the Uniform Credentialing Act who advises the department and carries out duties under the Statewide Trauma System Act.SourceLaws 1997, LB 626, ยง 31;Laws 1999, LB 594, ยง 63;Laws 2007, LB296, ยง 690;Laws 200
